# SoilSense - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in values
#
# NOTE: This app uses only FREE APIs by default:
#   - NASA POWER (no API key needed)
#   - ERA5 via Open-Meteo (no API key needed)
#   - OpenCV computer vision (local)
#
# If you want to add Groq AI-powered soil report analysis:
# 1. Sign up at https://console.groq.com (free tier: ~30 req/min)
# 2. Create an API key
# 3. Set it below:
#
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your_groq_api_key_here
#
# Flask settings
# FLASK_ENV=production
